HEADWORD: Jagua palm
<hw>Ja"gua palm`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[Sp. <ets>jagua</ets> the fruit
of the jagua palm.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A great Brazilian palm
